Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.47,0:24:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,月火Da☆Yo！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.59,0:24:12.38,NoteV,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\pos(1512,198)}月火DaYo！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.44,0:24:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,两个人合在一起就是Fire Sisters！
